Syntype, RMNH.AVES.87284, adult male, mounted skin. Loc.: Dongola, Nubia, [Sudan]. Leg.: [
Rueppell
].

An adult male which is depicted on pl. 141 in livraison 24 is in the NMW (NMW 39971; 
Schifter et al. 2007
: 81). However, pl. 141 appeared in July 1822, four months after pl. 116 (March 1822). The specimen illustrated on pl. 141 therefore has no type status.

